## Development

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/dhruvbhavsar0612/fastsql-project-setup.git
cd fastsql-project-setup

# Install dependencies
uv sync

# Run locally
uv run fastapi-smith

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Type checking
uv run mypy src

# Linting
uv run ruff check src
```

